featured_reviews.review_id:
Nicely decorated inside with love and care!

Outside, it doesn't look so good but internal is neat and clean and well maintained.

Remember that it's open for the honest people.

Pray for 5 times and fave faith in God/Allah.

Washroom/Ozukhana is available there to clean your external body parts (hands, feet, hair and face).

Make yourself clean and pray to Allah.

Note: Your mind should be holy(no biased) to pray to Allah.
